1
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:09,680
Mizuki.

2
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:11,010
Hinata!

3
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:12,640
You're back.

4
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,850
You're early today.

5
00:00:13,850 --> 00:00:18,270
Yeah, but I still have work to finish.

6
00:00:18,270 --> 00:00:19,940
Is that tonight's dinner?

7
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:22,520
I'm craving meat.

8
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,400
Oh, this is for camping tomorrow.

9
00:00:25,690 --> 00:00:27,490
Tomorrow? What about school?

10
00:00:27,490 --> 00:00:31,070
We have the day off, so I'm going camping.

11
00:00:31,070 --> 00:00:36,700
Must be nice. Students get so much time off.

12
00:00:37,290 --> 00:00:38,960
I still have to work tomorrow.

13
00:00:52,140 --> 00:00:54,390
Alright, alright.

14
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:12,860
You've never worked a job,
so you wouldn't understand.

15
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:18,240
Must be nice. Students get so much time off.

16
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,330
I still have to work tomorrow.

17
00:01:34,390 --> 00:01:35,260
Hinata.

18
00:01:35,890 --> 00:01:37,060
Kamiki-san?
